Website Under Test
URL: hhtps://www.saucedemo.com
Objective
---------
Automate key user scenarios using Selenium WebDriver with Python to validate functionality and UI behaviour.

Scenarios to Automate
1 Login Functionality
    Valid Login: Use standard user credentials.
2 Product Page Validation
    Verify product list loads correctly.
    validate sorting functionality (e.g. price low to high)
    Check product details page navigation.
3 Add to Cart
    Add multiple items to cart.
    Validate cart count and contents.
4 Checkout Process
    Fill in user information.
    Validate price summary.
    Complete purchase and verify confirmation.
5 Logout Functionality
    Ensure user can log out and is redirected to login page.

Tech Stack
----------
Language: Pyton
Framework: Selenium webdriver (Py-test)
Build Tool: Pycharm
Test Framework:
Design Pattern: Page Object Model(POM)

